title: Fort White rides Jackson passing TDs, tops Hilliard
text:
Fort White rides Jackson passing TDs, tops Hilliard 
Sat, Oct 10, 2015 @ 12:13 am 
FORT WHITE 36 
HILLIARD 20 
Fort White used a strong second quarter to overpower the host Red Flashes (2-4, 0-3) in District 6-1A play. ... Demetric Jackson Jr. threw two TDs to Bryson Brady and Nick McClain, his first passing touchdowns of the season for the Indians (4-2, 2-0).
